==Yang Metal Rat (庚子)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Sin|ja|辛}} and {{ill|Hei|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)}}), the month of {{ill|November|ja|11月}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月}} of {{ill|Koushi|ja|庚子}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Heavy Snow|ja|大雪}} until the day before {{ill|Lesser Cold|ja|小寒}}) as applicable.

==Yang Metal Rat (庚子)'s Days==
=== Selected Day (選日) ===
The day of {{ill|Koushi|ja|庚子}} is the 8th day of {{ill|Ten Ten Ichijō|ja|天一天上}}.

==See Also==
* {{ill|Metal Rat (Xiliang)|ja|庚子 (西涼)|lt=Metal Rat (Xiliang)|lt_ja=庚子 (西涼)}} – The era name of the dynasty of {{ill|China|ja|中国}}, during the {{ill|Five Hu Sixteen Kingdoms period|ja|五胡十六国時代}}, of the kingdom {{ill|Xiliang|ja|西涼}}, covering 400–404 AD.



