==Yang Metal Rat (庚子)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Sin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)}} and {{ill|Hei|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)}}), the month of {{ill|November|ja|11月}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月}} of {{ill|Koushi|ja|庚子}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Heavy Snow|ja|大雪}} until the day before {{ill|Lesser Cold|ja|小寒}}) as applicable.

