==Yang Metal Rat (庚子)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft}} are {{ill|Sin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Hei|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|November|ja|11月|12=draft|12=draft}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Koushi|ja|庚子|12=draft|12=draft}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Heavy Snow|ja|大雪|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Lesser Cold|ja|小寒|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.

==Yang Metal Rat (庚子)'s Days==
=== Selected Day (選日) ===
The day of {{ill|Koushi|ja|庚子|12=draft|12=draft}} is the 8th day of {{ill|Ten Ten Ichijō|ja|天一天上|12=draft|12=draft}}.

