It is the 37th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Kihai|ja|己亥|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Shinchuu|ja|辛丑|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Kou|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Metal|ja|金|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Rat|ja|子 (十二支)|lt=Rat|lt_ja=子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Water|ja|水|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, establishing a generating relationship ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|五行思想#相生（そうじょう）|lt=Mutual Generation|lt_ja=相生|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (Metal generates Water).  
==Yang Metal Rat (庚子)'s Years==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 40 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Koushi|ja|庚子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
