==Yang Metal Rat (庚子)'s Days==
=== Selected Day (選日) ===
The day of {{ill|Koushi|ja|庚子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is the 8th day of {{ill|Ten Ten Ichijō|ja|天一天上|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

