{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}}

'''Yang Metal Rat also known as 庚子''' (kanoene, koukin no nezumi, koukin no ne, koushi) is one of the elements of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.

It is the 37th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Kihai|ja|己亥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kihai|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Shinchuu|ja|辛丑|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinchuu|qq=}}. In the framework of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Kou|ja|庚|1=Kanoe (庚)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kou|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (庚)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Metal|ja|金|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Metal|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}} symbol {{ill|Rat|ja|子 (十二支)|lt=Rat|lt_ja=子|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rat|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Water|ja|水|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water|qq=}}, establishing a generating relationship ({{ill|Mutual Generation|ja|五行思想#相生（そうじょう）|lt=Mutual Generation|lt_ja=相生|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mutual Generation|qq=}}) (Metal generates Water).  
==Yang Metal Rat (庚子)'s Years==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} that leaves a remainder of 40 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/year|qq=}} of {{ill|Koushi|ja|庚子|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koushi|qq=}}.
