er Cold]]) as applicable. ==Days of Yang Metal Rat== ==Yang Metal Rat (庚子)'s Days== === Selected Day (選日) === The day of {{ill|Koushi|ja|1=Yang Metal Rat|2=ja|庚子|1=Yang Metal Rat|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koushi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koushi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Metal Rat|qq=}} is the 8th day of {{ill|Ten Ten Ichijō|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Ten Ichijō|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Ten Ichijō|qq=}}.
